<view class="page">
  <view class="intro">
    配置个人 Token，让 Agent 自动拉取你的会议日程和已结束会议的智能纪要。
  </view>

  <view class="step">
    <view class="step-num">1</view>
    <view class="step-body">
      <view class="step-title">访问腾讯会议 AI Skill 页面获取 Token</view>
      <view class="link-btn" bindtap="openAiSkill">
        复制 URL: meeting.tencent.com/ai-skill
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="step">
    <view class="step-num">2</view>
    <view class="step-body">
      <view class="step-title">粘贴 Token</view>
      <input
        class="token-input"
        value="{{token}}"
        bindinput="onTokenInput"
        placeholder="QZSQagk... " />
      <view class="actions">
        <view class="btn ghost {{testing ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="{{testing ? '' : 'onTest'}}">
          {{testing ? '测试中...' : '测试连接'}}
        </view>
        <view class="btn primary {{saving ? 'disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="{{saving ? '' : 'onSave'}}">
          {{saving ? '保存中...' : '保存'}}
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{testResult}}" class="test-result {{testOk ? 'ok' : 'fail'}}">
        {{testResult}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="warning">
    <view class="warn-title">⚠️ 重要提示</view>
    <view class="warn-body">
      拉取智能纪要需要会议**开启云录制**。个人版默认未开启，请在每场需要纪要的会议中手动开启。
    </view>
    <view class="link-btn" bindtap="openCloudRecordingDoc">
      📖 复制：如何开启云录制
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
